<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='910010' id='t-910010'>that also wouldn't be funny.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='911407' id='t-911407'>The fact that the laughter works,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='913069' id='t-913069'>it gets him from a painful,
