<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='919116' id='t-919116'>and I think that's 
a really interesting use,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='921303' id='t-921303'>and it's actually happening all the time.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='923281' id='t-923281'>For example, I can remember
something like this happening</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='925972' id='t-925972'>at my father's funeral.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='927169' id='t-927169'>We weren't jumping around
on the ice in our underpants.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929784' id='t-929784'>We're not Canadian.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='932425' id='t-932425'>(Laughter) (Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='934924' id='t-934924'>These events are always difficult, I had
