<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='965569' id='t-965569'>We're going to be okay.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='967065' id='t-967065'>And in fact, all of us
